===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: ruòròu qiángshí

===Etymology===
Literally: weak, meat, strong, eat
===Proverb===
'''[[弱]][[肉]][[强]][[食]]'''
#if you are weak, you are the meat; if you are strong, you eat the meat

